{"parse":{"title":"Leon Claire Metz","pageid":24790600,"revid":819387465,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\">This article is about the American cultural historian. For the Luxembourgian statesman and industrialist, see <a href=\"/wiki/L%C3%A9on_Metz\" title=\"L\u00e9on Metz\">L\u00e9on Metz</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"plainlinks metadata ambox ambox-content ambox-multiple_issues compact-ambox\" role=\"presentation\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"mbox-image\"><div style=\"width:52px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Ambox_important.svg/40px-Ambox_important.svg.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Ambox_important.svg/60px-Ambox_important.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Ambox_important.svg/80px-Ambox_important.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"40\" data-file-height=\"40\" /></div></td><td class=\"mbox-text\"><div class=\"mbox-text-span\"><div class=\"mw-collapsible\" style=\"width:95%; margin: 0.2em 0;\"><b>This article has multiple issues.</b> Please help <b><a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Leon_Claire_Metz&amp;action=edit\">improve it</a></b> or discuss these issues on the <b><a href=\"/wiki/Talk:Leon_Claire_Metz\" title=\"Talk:Leon Claire Metz\">talk page</a></b>. <small><i>(<a href=\"/wiki/Help:Maintenance_template_removal\" title=\"Help:Maintenance template removal\">Learn how and when to remove these template messages</a>)</i></small>\n<div class=\"mw-collapsible-content\" style=\"margin-top: 0.3em;\">\n      <table class=\"plainlinks metadata ambox ambox-content ambox-Notability\" role=\"presentation\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"mbox-image\"><div style=\"width:52px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Ambox_important.svg/40px-Ambox_important.svg.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedi